name: SurviveAggresiveBird
description:
11 y/o + angry birds + unity assets + nothing original + slender man = SurviveAggresiveBird.

So yeah this took 3 days to make the Pre-Alpha. Also yes, I know Aggressive is spelt wrong but its for the funnys.

I want to see people try to speedrun this idk why, and I wanna see youtubers play this too! (For Example: YuB, Bijuu Mike (I know I spelt that wrong) 8-Bit Ryan, and more.)
